name: Baia's boats
description:
Photographic typology.

Inspired by the thought of the couple Hilla and Bernd Becher “placed side by side, things acquire a correspondence. When arranged in a group, things that are barely  istinguishable from one another win individuality".

In this context, striking aspects, however, barely noticeable when analyzed individually, if they are of mystery and strength when put together. And precisely, in this scenario of multiple shapes, colors and textures, which unusual elements stand out.

contato@mateusmorbeck.com | twitter: @teumorbeck
